Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:47.08,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna시골b\fs50\bord7\fscx80\c&H79DDDC&\3c&H4F4F50&\frx0\fry358\frz0.3613\pos(585,415)}드링크 등을 절대 뿌리지 마세요!!{\fs20}\N\N{\fs50}기재가 파손됐을 경우, 변상을 요구할 수도 있습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:52.96,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna카툰\fs40\bord4\c&H090707&\3c&HE8D9B0&\pos(1002,964)}학교에서 있었던 이야기
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,그러고 보니\N두 분 다 같은 학교...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,맞아!\N시모고~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,둘 다, 집이 가까워서\N거기로 골랐어
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,아...\N시모키타자와에 거주하시는...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,어라?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩은\N슈카고라며?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,집, 이 근처 아냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,아
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,아니...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,현 밖에서 통학하는데...\N편도 2시간 거리예요...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:05.43,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(1638,644)}2시간…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐 하러??
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(525,980)}고등학교는 아무도 제 과거를\N모르는 곳으로 가고 싶어서...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(525,980)}네, 학기 끝~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,죄..죄송해요...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,고등학교에서도\N기본적으로는 혼자 다녀서...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,그...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,즐겁게 떠들썩한 이야기\N하나 제공 모...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,못해서...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮아, 괜찮아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,료..료도 말야~\N친구 그닥 없거든...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,응
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,니지카밖에 없어
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}엩...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.28,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,700)\fna두리둥실\fs80\bord5\blur5\3c&H8D31FF&\c&HEDB8FF&\move(840,760,830,750,00,1500)}뚝큰♥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}료 씨는...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나랑 동족이었구나...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:35.79,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(560,10)\fn@a유리구슬\b0\frz270\fs60\bord6\pos(1535,405)\c&H484D4C&\3c&HEBEFEF&}외톨이의 언덕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,쉬는 날에는\N혼자서 폐허 탐색하거나~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,헌옷집 탐방하거나~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아니, 아니야...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}료 씨는 혼자 사는 걸\N좋아하는 사람이다...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.47,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,00)\fna키즈\b0\fs80\bord4\c&H3524BD&\3c&H251D7F&\t(00,1040,\fscx70\fscy70)\frz14.88\move(1465,220,1375,235,00,1040)}찐따
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:48.93,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\fna키즈\b0\fs80\bord4\c&H3524BD&\3c&H251D7F&\fscx70\fscy70)\t(00,460,\fscx55\fscy55)\frz14.88\move(1375,235,1265,230,00,460)}찐따
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:49.22,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\fna키즈\b0\fs80\bord4\c&H3524BD&\3c&H251D7F&\fscx55\fscy55)\t(00,290,\fscx45\fscy45)\frz14.88\move(1265,230,1185,235,00,290)}찐따
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:49.89,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,10)\fna키즈\b0\fs80\bord4\c&H3524BD&\3c&H251D7F&\fscx45\fscy45)\t(00,670,\fscx40\fscy40)\frz14.88\move(1185,235,1152,240,00,670)}찐따
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.99,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,1100)\fna키즈\b0\fs45\bord4\c&H9073E3&\3c&H473479&\t(00,3100,\fscx90\fscy90)\t(2000,3100,\blur10)\move(1265,265,1240,275,00,3100)}혼자가 편함
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}커뮤장애는 혼자서\N옷가게 들어가지도 못하는데!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}"찐따"랑\N"혼자가 편한 사람" 사이에는...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}결코 메울 수 없는\N깊고 커다란 골이~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(630,980)}하마터면\N트랩에 걸릴 뻔 했어...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,980)}봇치쨩!\N대화를 좀 즐겨보자!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.99,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,100)\fna카툰\fs80\bord4\c&H090707&\3c&HE8D9B0&\frx2\fry4\frz5.708\pos(570,564)}학교에서 있었던 이야기
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:05.57,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna카툰\fs40\bord4\c&H090707&\3c&H75C8E1&\pos(1745,345)\frz346.5}좋아하는 음악 이야기
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,다음은\N좋아하는 음악 이야기~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,줄여서~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,음얘~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,으..음얘...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,나는 있지!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,멜로딕 하드코어 같은\N소위, 재패니즈 펑크려나~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord3\pos(866,836)}멜로코어
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,나는\N테크노 가요라든가
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,요즘은 사우디아라비아의\N히트 차트를...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,거기,\N구라 치지 마시고~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,진짜다, 뭐...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩은?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,그게...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,청춘 컴플렉스를 자극하는\N노래만 아니라면...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐든...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,응?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,청춘 컴플렉스...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,설명하지~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.85,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\fs50\bord7\pos(960,545)\c&H474445&\3c&HFAFAFA&}~기타오의 알기 쉬운 찐따 강좌~\N\N{\fna카툰\fs90}청춘 컴플렉스편
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,청춘 컴플렉스를\N자극하는 노래라는 건~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,여름이라든가\N푸른 바다!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,불꽃놀이!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,아련한 사랑 같은~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,찐따 학교 생활이랑은\N전혀 연관 없는 워드로 점철돼서!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}반짝반짝하게 코팅된\N상큼한 노래를 말하는 것이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그런 가사를 듣고 있으면\N세상 우울해져...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.91,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\fna두리둥실\fs60\move(410,650,465,650,00,2030)}이보세요~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.28,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\fna두리둥실\fs60\move(500,650,555,650,00,2000)}봇치쨩…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.54,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\fna두리둥실\fs60\move(550,650,605,650,00,2000)}저기요~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,반대로!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,청춘시대의 울분을 가사에\N때려박는 밴드는 진짜 좋지~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:05:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,응, 응~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,하지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,좋아하던 밴드가 학창시절부터\N인기 많았단 걸 알게 되면...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,갑자기 멀찍한 존재처럼\N여겨지기도 해서...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,즈어기~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,부탁 좀 하자~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,혼자만의 세계에\N기어들어가지 말자~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,어이!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,어여...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,어...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,여보세요~!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,다들, 결속 좀 하자~!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,결속밴드인 만큼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.23,Default - A,,0,0,0,,록이란 건\N비참한 패배자가 부르니까
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.89,Default - A,,0,0,0,,마음 속에 울리는 거지
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.79,Default - A,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,500)}성공한 사람이 부르면\N그건 더 이상 록이라고는 하지 않지...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.73,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna카툰\fs90\bord4\c&H090707&\3c&H7F74DE&\pos(970,590)}라이브 이야기
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 보자~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,첫라이브는\Ninst.였지만
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,다음은\N보컬을 넣고 싶거든~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 그러셨나요...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,원래는 도망친 기타 담당 애가\N부를 예정이었는데~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,걔는\N어딜 가버린 걸까?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}도망친 기타 담당...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나랑 똑같이\N커뮤장애였던 걸까...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs100}아니, 아니네!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(958.89,981.26)}진짜 커뮤장애는\N도망치는 것도 쉽지 않다!!
