Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,보컬\N또 찾아야겠네~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,나는 노래라면\N잼병이구...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 봇치쨩은...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,아니...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,아하하...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,그치~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,저..저기, 료 씨는...?
