Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,프론트맨까지 했다간...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,그냥 내 원맨이 돼버려서\N밴드를 박살내고 말 거야~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,그 근거 없이 솟아나는\N자신감 대체 뭐임?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}부럽다...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}저 자신감\N좀 나눠줬으면...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,맞다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,보컬 찾아내면\N곡도 만들자구!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,료는\N작곡 할 줄 아니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,가사에 피하고 싶은 말이 많다면\N봇치쨩이 쓰면 되잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}내가요!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,어때?\N좋은 생각 아냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}초, 중 9년간...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}쉬는 시간을 도서실에서\N계속 보냈던 것은
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이를 위한 포석이었다...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,니지카는\N뭘 할 건데?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,에잇~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,다음은\N목표치 이야기~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,당당하게 흘려넘겼다
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 저기...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,목표치라는 건...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,어제 나갔던 라이브는\N「부킹 라이브」라고 하는데
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,밴드 측에는 라이브 하우스 쪽에서\N집객을 보장하기 위한
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,티켓 목표치가\N부과되는데~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:52.95,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,00)\fna천생연분\fs60\bord7\pos(1030,515)\fscx1\fscy1\t(00,100,\fscx120\fscy120)\t(100,200,\fscx90\fscy90)\t(200,300,\fscx100\fscy100)}달성 목표는{\fs20}\N\N{\fs60}10장!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:53.25,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,300)\fna천생연분\fs60\bord7\move(1030,515,1530,515,00,300)}달성 목표는{\fs20}\N\N{\fs60}10장!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,목표치를 넘기고\N남은 수익은
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,라이브 하우스랑\N밴드가 나눠갖지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,목표치만큼\N집객하지 못한 경우에는
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,그만큼\N사비로 때워야 하거든~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,즉, 히트 칠 때까지는\N돈 무지막지 깨져
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}신랄하게 요약했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,어제 라이브는\N내 친구들이 꽤 와줘서
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,티켓 땜빵 좀 했지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,그 퀄리티에\N2번 보러 오진 않지
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,그치~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,료는 친구가 없으니까\N집객은 기대할 수가 없구
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩은~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,응, 미안!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮으니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,죽은 동태 눈깔\N하지 말자!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}상상 친구라면\N잔뜩 있는데 말야아아
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs40\bord4\pos(904,836)}이매지너리 프렌드
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,10)\fscy70\t(00,100,\fscy150)\t(100,200,\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscy100)\fna두리둥실\fs70\frz337\pos(1482.667,633.333)}히토리쨩\N최고~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,10)\fscy70\t(00,100,\fscy150)\t(100,200,\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscy100)\fna두리둥실\fs70\frz15.2\pos(389.334,801.333)}올! 인간국보~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇게 된 거라!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,당분간 라이브 할 때마다\N몇 만 엔은 필요하니까
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,목표 땜빵비, 기재 대여료\N등등 벌기 위해서
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}알바 하자~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,옙...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscy50\t(00,100,\fscy200)\t(100,200,\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscy100)\fs120}알바!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘 들은 것 중에\N목소리 제일 크다?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:08:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}절-대로 싫어!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}일하고 싶지 않아
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}무서워!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}사회가 무섭다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,응...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,돼지 저금통?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,저..저희 어머니께서...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,제 결혼 비용이라면서\N모아주시는 건데...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,이걸로 부디...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,알바만큼은~!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,우리를\N인간 쓰레기로 만들려고!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.61,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,00)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(1255,690)}고마워
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:18.96,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,300)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(1255,690)}감사히 잘 쓸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,어딜 손을 대, 손을!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,그런 소중한 돈을\N어떻게 쓰겠어~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:22.82,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1390,980)}우...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1390,980)}우, 아...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1390,980)}그치만...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(1390,980)}일하고 싶지 않아!!
