Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,진짜!?\N고마워~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:35.16,Default - A,,0,0,0,,알바도 떠들썩해져서\N더 즐거워지겠네!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}미안하다, 친구야...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs43\bord3\pos(1041,910)}나
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}거절할 용기가 있었으면\N커뮤장애도 안 생겼지...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,그리고 밴드 경비는\N내가 관리할게
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,예...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,저..저기...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,료 씨한테 맡기는 게\N좋지 않을지...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,거 뭔 뜻이고!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,있잖아, 봇치쨩...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,료는 이렇게 보여도\N완전 흥청망청 돈 쓴다구
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,부자라서\N용돈도 잔뜩 받는데
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,죄다 악기에 들이부으니까\N항상 돈에 쪼들린다구~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:59.27,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,600)\fna두리둥실\fs90\bord5\move(495,865,485,855,00,1400)}부끄♡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,대체 어느 부분이\N칭찬으로 들린 것이지?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,가까운 시일 내로\N또 라이브 할 수 있게 힘 내자~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,그리고 고등학생 신분으로\N메이저 데뷔~!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,알바는\N다음주부터다♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,학교 끝나면\N우리 가게로 바로 오기!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치, 바이바이
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,옙...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그래서
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그 알바 첫날이\N내일로 다가왔다는...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}벌써 30분은\N몸 담고 있었으니깐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}보나마나\N감기 걸렸겠지!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}미안합니다, 죄송합니다
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}알바만 빼고는\N열심히 할 테니...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 엄마~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,언니가\N가라앉고 있어~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,우오오오!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,감기 걸려라!
