Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,너나 진정하고
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,새로 온다는\N알바 애였나
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 처음부터\N그렇다고 말을 하라고
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,죄..죄송합니다...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,나, 여기 점장이니까\N잘 부탁하고
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,자...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,잘 부탁드립니다...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}점장님, 좀 무서워...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}거북한 타입인데...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}니지카쨩, 얼른 와줘~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:20.86,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna두리둥실\pos(1055,585)\fs80}어라?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,보니까 골판지 상자에 들어가서\N라이브하던 기타 애잖아
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,이름이 아마...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,망고 가면?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}새 별명...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}점장님 쪼아~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,마..망고 가면이에여~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs90}그런 이름 아니잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,언니도 대충\N별명 붙이지 말라구~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(815,980)}언니!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(815,980)}니지카쨩의\N언니분...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(815,980)}전에 설명했잖아?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(815,980)}그 왜,\N스태리 오는 길에
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}오늘 출연할 라이브 하우스는\N「STARRY」라고 하는데 말야!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}우리 언니가\N거기 점장을 하고 있어서~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}그보다 가게 위 맨션에\N우리 가족이 사는데~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아아...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,400)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}심장이 쿵쾅거려서\N못 듣고 있던 거네...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,그...\N그, 그, 그랬습니다...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,그런 고로~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,그러니까\N그렇게 막 긴장 안 해도 돼!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,그치, 언니~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,여기서는\N"점장님"이라고 불러라
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,그리고 일하는 데에\N개인감정 끼워넣지 마라
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,600)\fscy70\t(00,100,\fscy150)\t(100,200,\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscy100)\fna두리둥실\frz350.8\pos(1550,380)}힉!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,진짜~\N괜히 겁주지 말라구~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.87,Above - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna카툰\fs80\bord5\c&H7F77B5&\3c&HE5E5E5&\frx354\fry24\frz18.17\pos(690,290)}착한 아이\N사과100
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,우선은\N테이블부터 정리할까~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,그 다음에는\N걸레질을~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,근데...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,어라?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩은?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,죄송해요...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,어둑하고 좁은 곳에서\N숨 좀 돌리고 싶어서...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐 했다고\N벌써 힘들어 해!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 봇치쨩은~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,여기서\N드링크나 외워볼까?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,토닉 워터는\N여기서 꺼내고~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,맥주는\N이 서버다?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,칵테일은\N뒷쪽 찬장에~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:43.94,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,00)\fscy70\t(00,100,\fscy150)\t(100,200,\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscy100)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(880,405)}으어어…!
