Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HF2&\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(958.64,978.68)}으버버어버버버버즈버어
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}노래로 만들어서\N몸에 새겨두는 수밖에...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs120}없다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,으어어!?\N어디서 꺼낸 거야??
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.98,Default - A,,0,0,0,,♪칵테일은~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.59,Default - A,,0,0,0,,♪찬장 오른쪽에서~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:02.28,Default - A,,0,0,0,,♪데킬라!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:02.99,Default - A,,0,0,0,,♪보드카!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:03.65,Default - A,,0,0,0,,♪칼루아!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:04.52,Default - A,,0,0,0,,♪럼~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:01.18,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(935,280)}즐거워 보이네요~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,에에!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 어어...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,무서, 무섭게...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,외우려고\N노력해주는 건 기쁜데...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,일단...\N기타 좀 내려놓을까...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:05.66,Default - A,,0,0,0,,응...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:06.31,Default - A,,0,0,0,,저기...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:07.51,Default - A,,0,0,0,,듣고 있니...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.58,Default - A,,0,0,0,,안 듣고 있구나!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:09.58,Default - A,,0,0,0,,어, 잠깐...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:10.45,Default - A,,0,0,0,,제발...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.91,Default - A,,0,0,0,,진짜 무서워지기\N시작했거든!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.57,Default - A,,0,0,0,,어어어어...\N부탁이니까...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:15.62,Default - A,,0,0,0,,정신 차리자!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.31,Default - A,,0,0,0,,히..히토리쨩...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.49,Default - A,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}히토리쨔아아앙!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,어라...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,저번 라이브 때는\N허접해 보이더니...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,잘 치네요~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}니지카는 말리느라 정신 없어서\N눈치 못 챈 모양인데...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}이 연주하는 그루브는\N어디선가...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,일이나 해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,왜 내가 맞지...??
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,드링크 스태프는~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,주문받은 드링크를 따라서\N넘겨주기만 하면 되니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 옙...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,티켓 요금이랑은 별도로\N500엔 내면 받을 수 있는데
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,이게\N드링크 티켓이야!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}한 잔에\N500엔이라니...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}애초에 왜 원 드링크\N시스템인 걸까...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇게 노골적으로\N바가지 아니냐는 표정 하지 말자...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,사실, 라이브 하우스는\N일단 음식점 취급이거든
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,어...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,잘은 모르겠는데
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,라이브 할 수 있는 장소란 것만으로\N영업 허가를 받는 게 엄청 어렵대!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,그..그렇구나!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,그래서\N드링크를 제공해서~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,어디까지나 음식점으로\N가게를 여는 거래~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,근데, 듣고 있니?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:10.90,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fn@a유리구슬\b0\frz270\fs60\bord6\pos(1535,405)\c&H484D4C&\3c&HEBEFEF&}외톨이의 언덕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어..어느새 난이도 높다는\N음식점 알바 데뷔까지 끝냈다니~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}성장했어!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,아!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,어느샌가\N손님들 들어왔네~♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:19.33,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fn@a유리구슬\b0\frz270\fs60\bord6\pos(1535,405)\c&H484D4C&\3c&HEBEFEF&\t(00,4500,\c&H2D2F2F&\3c&HA2A5A5&)}외톨이의 언덕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩!\N이제부터 바빠질 거야~♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)}엩?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}예??
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}뜬금없이\N접객을 시작해!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}뭐라고 해야 하는데...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}오늘은 일진도 좋고\N방문해주셔서―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs90\pos(952.96,975.04)}..는 아니고!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs90\pos(958.24,983.52)}..는 아니고!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs90\pos(967.76,975.68)}..는 아니고!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs90\pos(965.76,987.44)}..는 아니고!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs90}..는 아니고!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}하..하다못해\N예행 연습 한 번만...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어, 아..아니!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}자..잠깐만...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}기다려보라구!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.80,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,100)\fna카툰\fs50\bord6\pos(1175,685)\c&H292E36&\3c&HE7E9E9&}오늘 영업은 끝났습니다{\fs20}\N\N{\fs50}감사합니다
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,하아...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,종료해버렸네!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,저기요~\N콜라 주세요
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,네~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩, 콜라~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,나는 진저에일
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩!\N손님들한테 실례잖아!!
