Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}끝나뜨아아아!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어찌저찌\N하루는 넘겼어~!
