Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,엣취!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,엉...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치,\N열심히 하더라
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,그러게~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,게다가...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,내일 또 보자고\N해줬지~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,응
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,밴드 결성하길\N참 잘했지~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 맞다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩한테\N로인 톡 보내두자!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,내일도\N열심히 하자고~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:38.94,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(230,10)\fna천생연분\fs30\pos(770,635)\c&H9C9B9D&\3c&HFFFFFF&}니지카\N\N신규 메시지가 있습니다.
