Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이제 와서 열이...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩도\N도와주고 있으니깐~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,남은 건...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)}새로운 보컬을\N찾아내는 것만 남았다~!
